(4951, 135, 'content_8_color', 'mint'),
(4952, 135, '_content_8_color', 'field_65e65f7a93338'),
(4953, 135, 'content_8_slides_0_img', '111'),
(4954, 135, '_content_8_slides_0_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4955, 135, 'content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'Inés Garza'),
(4956, 135, '_content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4957, 135, 'content_8_slides_0_sub', '10+ YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(4958, 135, '_content_8_slides_0_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4959, 135, 'content_8_slides_0_txt', 'She has a certification of 300 hours in Hatha Vinyasa and 100 advanced hours with Fabian Montes de Oca.\r\n\r\nInés firmly believes that yoga is a constant practice in which you never stop learning.\r\nThe important thing is to implement the enormous tools it gives us, off the mat. Like self-knowledge and mental clarity, which undoubtedly come from being constant.'),
(4960, 135, '_content_8_slides_0_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(4961, 135, 'content_8_slides_1_img', '105'),
(4962, 135, '_content_8_slides_1_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4963, 135, 'content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'Ana Sofia Benavides'),
(4964, 135, '_content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4965, 135, 'content_8_slides_1_sub', ''),
(4966, 135, '_content_8_slides_1_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4967, 135, 'content_8_slides_1_txt', 'Ana got certified with Middle Path Movement in Sayulita, Nayarit as a Hatha Yoga and Vinyasa instructor. She is a reiki therapist and meditation coach. In her classes, she focuses on strengthening the body and mind through meditation, fluid movement, and conscious breathing. Each posture becomes an opportunity to reconnect with your body and find your internal balance.'),
(4968, 135, '_content_8_slides_1_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(4969, 135, 'content_8_slides_2_img', '113'),
(4970, 135, '_content_8_slides_2_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4971, 135, 'content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'Karla Garza'),
(4972, 135, '_content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4973, 135, 'content_8_slides_2_sub', '13 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(4974, 135, '_content_8_slides_2_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4975, 135, 'content_8_slides_2_txt', 'She was certified with Cristina Loyola in Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced Pilates Reformer and Pilates Mat. In 2022 Karla founded Reform Studio, giving private classes from her home.'),
(4976, 135, '_content_8_slides_2_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(4977, 135, 'content_8_slides_3_img', '83'),
(4978, 135, '_content_8_slides_3_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4979, 135, 'content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'Cecilia Cepeda'),
(4980, 135, '_content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4981, 135, 'content_8_slides_3_sub', '17 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(4982, 135, '_content_8_slides_3_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4983, 135, 'content_8_slides_3_txt', 'Yoga came into my life completely transforming it, allowing me to develop more physical strength, but at the same time working on my physical and mental flexibility.\r\nI got certified in Vinyasa 6 years ago and I have done other specialties in Anatomy and Biomechanics because I find the body fascinating and knowing more about it inspires me a lot.\r\nMy classes are multi-level Vinyasa flow, with variations for everyone, working the body with great awareness and connecting with the mind through breathing and movement.'),
(4984, 135, '_content_8_slides_3_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(4985, 135, 'content_8_slides_4_img', '107'),
(4986, 135, '_content_8_slides_4_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4987, 135, 'content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'Andrea Edde'),
(4988, 135, '_content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4989, 135, 'content_8_slides_4_sub', '8 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(4990, 135, '_content_8_slides_4_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4991, 135, 'content_8_slides_4_txt', 'Passionate about movement. Their mission is to motivate others to honor and celebrate the body for what it can do. With over 8 years of experience as a Yoga &amp; Pilates teacher, she creates training sessions for a variety of clients based on their physical condition, injuries and goals.\r\n\r\nAndrea teaches the Pilates repertoire in private, couples and group settings using all equipment including the reformer, cadillac, Wunda chair, plank and mat. She also teaches yoga flows for beginners, focusing mostly on vinyasa and power yoga.'),
(4992, 135, '_content_8_slides_4_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(4993, 135, 'content_8_slides_5_img', '108'),
(4994, 135, '_content_8_slides_5_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(4995, 135, 'content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'Belen Jiménez'),
(4996, 135, '_content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(4997, 135, 'content_8_slides_5_sub', '3 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(4998, 135, '_content_8_slides_5_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(4999, 135, 'content_8_slides_5_txt', 'Belen loves all things related to health. She has been involved in the medical sector for more than 15 years and that led her to become certified as a Pilates instructor.\r\n\r\nShe has been teaching pilates reformer, Wunda chair and mat classes for 3 years. She is certified by Alves pilates in mat, reformer, barrel, chair, cadillac and low barrels and also by Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced reformer. Belen loves to see the progress of the students and see how they are improving in safety, posture, injuries, etc.'),
(5000, 135, '_content_8_slides_5_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(5001, 135, 'content_8_slides_6_img', '83'),
(5002, 135, '_content_8_slides_6_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(5003, 135, 'content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'Rodrigo Castillo'),
(5004, 135, '_content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(5005, 135, 'content_8_slides_6_sub', '14 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(5006, 135, '_content_8_slides_6_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(5007, 135, 'content_8_slides_6_txt', 'Reality is not how it happened, but how we remember it. Creator of experiences, negotiator, I listen to all the NOs and then I explore and build with what YES, you have, you can, if there is as a team, achieve your goals together.'),
(5008, 135, '_content_8_slides_6_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(5009, 135, 'content_8_slides_7_img', '104'),
(5010, 135, '_content_8_slides_7_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(5011, 135, 'content_8_slides_7_ttl', 'Alexandra Barzana'),
(5012, 135, '_content_8_slides_7_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(5013, 135, 'content_8_slides_7_sub', '6 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(5014, 135, '_content_8_slides_7_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(5015, 135, 'content_8_slides_7_txt', 'Alexandra began practicing at the age of 16 and at the age of 26 she traveled to India where she practiced with Saraswathi Jois and B.N.S Iyengar in the city of Mysore and with Sharath Jois in the city of Rishikesh. In 2018 she trained as a licensed yoga teacher at Nepal Yoga Home in Kathmandu.\r\n\r\nIn 2020, going through the pandemic, she came across the pilates mat method and became fascinated. In 2021 she trained as a Pilates teacher with teacher Elsa Monterd, founder of the Lumin Pilates school.'),
(5016, 135, '_content_8_slides_7_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(5017, 135, 'content_8_slides_8_img', '109'),
(5018, 135, '_content_8_slides_8_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(5019, 135, 'content_8_slides_8_ttl', 'Camilla Garza'),
(5020, 135, '_content_8_slides_8_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(5021, 135, 'content_8_slides_8_sub', '10 YEARS EXPERIENCE'),
(5022, 135, '_content_8_slides_8_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(5023, 135, 'content_8_slides_8_txt', 'She was certified in Balance in Motion with Cristina Loyola in basic and intermediate Pilates Reformer and also in Pilates Mat. Camilla began giving private classes from her home along with her sister, Karla. She thus founded Reform Studio.'),
