(6052, 152, '_content_8_ttl', 'field_65e659be9a316'),
(6053, 152, 'content_8_color', 'mint'),
(6054, 152, '_content_8_color', 'field_65e65f7a93338'),
(6055, 152, 'content_8_slides_0_img', '111'),
(6056, 152, '_content_8_slides_0_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6057, 152, 'content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'Inés Garza'),
(6058, 152, '_content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6059, 152, 'content_8_slides_0_sub', ''),
(6060, 152, '_content_8_slides_0_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6061, 152, 'content_8_slides_0_txt', 'Inés firmly believes that yoga is a constant practice in which you never stop learning.\r\nThe important thing is to implement the enormous tools it gives us, off the mat. Like self-knowledge and mental clarity, which undoubtedly come from being constant.\r\n\r\nShe has a certification of 300 hours in Hatha Vinyasa and 100 advanced hours with Fabian Montes de Oca.'),
(6062, 152, '_content_8_slides_0_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6063, 152, 'content_8_slides_1_img', '105'),
(6064, 152, '_content_8_slides_1_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6065, 152, 'content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'Ana Sofia Benavides'),
(6066, 152, '_content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6067, 152, 'content_8_slides_1_sub', ''),
(6068, 152, '_content_8_slides_1_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6069, 152, 'content_8_slides_1_txt', 'Ana got certified with Middle Path Movement in Sayulita, Nayarit as a Hatha Yoga and Vinyasa instructor. She is a reiki therapist and meditation coach. In her classes, she focuses on strengthening the body and mind through meditation, fluid movement, and conscious breathing. Each posture becomes an opportunity to reconnect with your body and find your internal balance.'),
(6070, 152, '_content_8_slides_1_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6071, 152, 'content_8_slides_2_img', '113'),
(6072, 152, '_content_8_slides_2_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6073, 152, 'content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'Karla Garza'),
(6074, 152, '_content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6075, 152, 'content_8_slides_2_sub', ''),
(6076, 152, '_content_8_slides_2_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6077, 152, 'content_8_slides_2_txt', 'Karla was certified with Cristina Loyola in Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced Pilates Reformer and Pilates Mat. In 2022 Karla founded Reform Studio, teaching private classes from her home.'),
(6078, 152, '_content_8_slides_2_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6079, 152, 'content_8_slides_3_img', '83'),
(6080, 152, '_content_8_slides_3_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6081, 152, 'content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'Cecilia Cepeda'),
(6082, 152, '_content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6083, 152, 'content_8_slides_3_sub', ''),
(6084, 152, '_content_8_slides_3_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6085, 152, 'content_8_slides_3_txt', 'Yoga came into Cecilia\'s life completely transforming it, allowing me to develop more physical strength, but at the same time working on my physical and mental flexibility.\r\nShe got certified in Vinyasa 6 years ago and has done other specialties in Anatomy and Biomechanics.\r\nHer classes are multi-level Vinyasa flow, with variations for everyone, working the body with great awareness and connecting with the mind through breathing and movement.'),
(6086, 152, '_content_8_slides_3_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6087, 152, 'content_8_slides_4_img', '107'),
(6088, 152, '_content_8_slides_4_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6089, 152, 'content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'Andrea Edde'),
(6090, 152, '_content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6091, 152, 'content_8_slides_4_sub', ''),
(6092, 152, '_content_8_slides_4_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6093, 152, 'content_8_slides_4_txt', 'Passionate about movement. Andrea\'s mission is to motivate others to honor and celebrate the body for what it can do. With over 8 years of experience as a Yoga &amp; Pilates teacher, she creates training sessions for a variety of clients based on their physical condition, injuries and goals.\r\n\r\nAndrea teaches the Pilates repertoire using the reformer and the mat.'),
(6094, 152, '_content_8_slides_4_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6095, 152, 'content_8_slides_5_img', '108'),
(6096, 152, '_content_8_slides_5_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6097, 152, 'content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'Belen Jiménez'),
(6098, 152, '_content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6099, 152, 'content_8_slides_5_sub', ''),
(6100, 152, '_content_8_slides_5_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6101, 152, 'content_8_slides_5_txt', 'Belen loves all things related to health. She has been involved in the medical sector for more than 15 years and that led her to become certified as a Pilates instructor.\r\n\r\nShe has been teaching pilates reformer, Wunda chair and mat classes for 3 years. She is certified by Alves pilates in mat, reformer, barrel, chair, cadillac and low barrels and also by Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced reformer.'),
(6102, 152, '_content_8_slides_5_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6103, 152, 'content_8_slides_6_img', '83'),
(6104, 152, '_content_8_slides_6_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6105, 152, 'content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'Rodrigo Castillo'),
(6106, 152, '_content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6107, 152, 'content_8_slides_6_sub', ''),
(6108, 152, '_content_8_slides_6_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6109, 152, 'content_8_slides_6_txt', 'Reality is not how it happened, but how we remember it. Creator of experiences, negotiator, I listen to all the NOs and then I explore and build with what YES, you have, you can, if there is as a team, achieve your goals together.'),
(6110, 152, '_content_8_slides_6_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6111, 152, 'content_8_slides_7_img', '104'),
(6112, 152, '_content_8_slides_7_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6113, 152, 'content_8_slides_7_ttl', 'Alexandra Barzana'),
(6114, 152, '_content_8_slides_7_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6115, 152, 'content_8_slides_7_sub', ''),
(6116, 152, '_content_8_slides_7_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6117, 152, 'content_8_slides_7_txt', 'Alexandra began practicing at the age of 16 and at the age of 26 she traveled to India where she practiced with Saraswathi Jois and B.N.S Iyengar in the city of Mysore and with Sharath Jois in the city of Rishikesh. In 2018 she trained as a licensed yoga teacher at Nepal Yoga Home in Kathmandu.\r\n\r\nIn 2020, she came across the pilates mat method and became fascinated. In 2021 she trained as a Pilates teacher with teacher Elsa Monterd, founder of the Lumin Pilates school.'),
(6118, 152, '_content_8_slides_7_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6119, 152, 'content_8_slides_8_img', '109'),
(6120, 152, '_content_8_slides_8_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6121, 152, 'content_8_slides_8_ttl', 'Camilla Garza'),
(6122, 152, '_content_8_slides_8_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6123, 152, 'content_8_slides_8_sub', ''),
(6124, 152, '_content_8_slides_8_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6125, 152, 'content_8_slides_8_txt', 'Camilla got certified in Balance in Motion with Cristina Loyola in basic and intermediate Pilates Reformer and also in Pilates Mat. Camilla began giving private classes from her home along with her sister, Karla. She thus founded Reform Studio.'),
(6126, 152, '_content_8_slides_8_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6127, 152, 'content_8_slides_9_img', '106'),
(6128, 152, '_content_8_slides_9_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6129, 152, 'content_8_slides_9_ttl', 'Ana'),
(6130, 152, '_content_8_slides_9_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6131, 152, 'content_8_slides_9_sub', ''),
(6132, 152, '_content_8_slides_9_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6133, 152, 'content_8_slides_9_txt', ''),
(6134, 152, '_content_8_slides_9_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6135, 152, 'content_8_slides_10_img', '110'),
(6136, 152, '_content_8_slides_10_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6137, 152, 'content_8_slides_10_ttl', 'Eugenia'),
(6138, 152, '_content_8_slides_10_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6139, 152, 'content_8_slides_10_sub', ''),
(6140, 152, '_content_8_slides_10_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6141, 152, 'content_8_slides_10_txt', 'Eugenia began her career as a pilates student in 2017. In love with the method, she decided to get certified and make her life purpose. She was trained under the oldest pilates teacher certification program in the world, based entirely on the original work of Joseph Pilates. As an instructor she seeks to strengthen and correct through contrology. Her classic class is  based on authentic pilates, while her flow and burn classes are a combination of classic and contemporaty pilates both on the reformer and on the mat.'),
(6142, 152, '_content_8_slides_10_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(6143, 152, 'content_8_slides_11_img', '112'),
(6144, 152, '_content_8_slides_11_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(6145, 152, 'content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'Irasema'),
(6146, 152, '_content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(6147, 152, 'content_8_slides_11_sub', ''),
(6148, 152, '_content_8_slides_11_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(6149, 152, 'content_8_slides_11_txt', 'Irasema currently works as a coach specialized in pilates reformer as well as pilates mat. Her focus has always been to connect the body with the mind efficiently and dynamically, seeking to provide students with the best possible experience. The greatest satisfaction she gets from teaching her classes is seeing the smiles on her students\' faces.'),
(6150, 152, '_content_8_slides_11_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
