(8283, 163, 'content_8_slides_0_img', '111'),
(8284, 163, '_content_8_slides_0_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8285, 163, 'content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'Inés Garza'),
(8286, 163, '_content_8_slides_0_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8287, 163, 'content_8_slides_0_sub', ''),
(8288, 163, '_content_8_slides_0_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8289, 163, 'content_8_slides_0_txt', 'She firmly believes that yoga is a constant practice in which one never stops learning. They hold a 300-hour certification in Hatha Vinyasa and 100 advanced hours with Fabian Montes de Oca.'),
(8290, 163, '_content_8_slides_0_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8291, 163, 'content_8_slides_1_img', '105'),
(8292, 163, '_content_8_slides_1_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8293, 163, 'content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'Ana Sofia Benavides'),
(8294, 163, '_content_8_slides_1_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8295, 163, 'content_8_slides_1_sub', ''),
(8296, 163, '_content_8_slides_1_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8297, 163, 'content_8_slides_1_txt', 'Ana got certified with Middle Path Movement in Sayulita, Nayarit, as a Hatha Yoga and Vinyasa instructor. In her classes, she focuses on strengthening the body and mind through  meditation, fluid movement and conscious breathing.'),
(8298, 163, '_content_8_slides_1_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8299, 163, 'content_8_slides_2_img', '113'),
(8300, 163, '_content_8_slides_2_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8301, 163, 'content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'Karla Garza'),
(8302, 163, '_content_8_slides_2_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8303, 163, 'content_8_slides_2_sub', ''),
(8304, 163, '_content_8_slides_2_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8305, 163, 'content_8_slides_2_txt', 'Karla got certified with Cristina Loyola at Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced Pilates Reformer, as well as Pilates Mat. In 2022, Karla founded Reform Studio, offering private classes from her home.'),
(8306, 163, '_content_8_slides_2_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8307, 163, 'content_8_slides_3_img', '83'),
(8308, 163, '_content_8_slides_3_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8309, 163, 'content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'Cecilia Cepeda'),
(8310, 163, '_content_8_slides_3_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8311, 163, 'content_8_slides_3_sub', ''),
(8312, 163, '_content_8_slides_3_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8313, 163, 'content_8_slides_3_txt', 'Cecilia got certified in Vinyasa sic years ago and has pursued other specialties in Anatomy and Biomechanics. Her classes are Vinyasa flow multilevel, with variations for everyone, working the body with great awareness and connecting with the mind through breathing and movement.'),
(8314, 163, '_content_8_slides_3_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8315, 163, 'content_8_slides_4_img', '107'),
(8316, 163, '_content_8_slides_4_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8317, 163, 'content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'Andrea Edde'),
(8318, 163, '_content_8_slides_4_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8319, 163, 'content_8_slides_4_sub', ''),
(8320, 163, '_content_8_slides_4_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8321, 163, 'content_8_slides_4_txt', 'With over 8 years of experience as a Yoga &amp; Pilates instructor, she creates training sessions for a variety of clients based on their fitness level, injuries and goals. Andrea teaches the Pilates repertoire in group settings using all equipment, including the reformer and mat.'),
(8322, 163, '_content_8_slides_4_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8323, 163, 'content_8_slides_5_img', '108'),
(8324, 163, '_content_8_slides_5_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8325, 163, 'content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'Belen Jiménez'),
(8326, 163, '_content_8_slides_5_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8327, 163, 'content_8_slides_5_sub', ''),
(8328, 163, '_content_8_slides_5_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8329, 163, 'content_8_slides_5_txt', 'Belen has been teaching Pilates reformer, wunda chair and mat classes for three years. She is certified by Alves Pilates in mat, reformer, chair, cadillac and by Balance in Motion in basic, intermediate and advanced reformer.'),
(8330, 163, '_content_8_slides_5_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8331, 163, 'content_8_slides_6_img', '83'),
(8332, 163, '_content_8_slides_6_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8333, 163, 'content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'Rodrigo Castillo'),
(8334, 163, '_content_8_slides_6_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8335, 163, 'content_8_slides_6_sub', ''),
(8336, 163, '_content_8_slides_6_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8337, 163, 'content_8_slides_6_txt', 'Reality is not how it happened, but how we remember it. Creator of experiences, negotiator, I listen to all the NOs and then I explore and build with what YES, you have, you can, if there is as a team, achieve your goals together.'),
(8338, 163, '_content_8_slides_6_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8339, 163, 'content_8_slides_7_img', '104'),
(8340, 163, '_content_8_slides_7_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
