(8368, 163, '_content_8_slides_10_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8369, 163, 'content_8_slides_10_txt', 'Eugenia began her career as a pilates student in 2017. In love with the method, she decided to get certified and make her life purpose. She was trained under the oldest pilates teacher certification program in the world, based entirely on the original work of Joseph Pilates. As an instructor she seeks to strengthen and correct through contrology. Her classic class is  based on authentic pilates, while her flow and burn classes are a combination of classic and contemporaty pilates both on the reformer and on the mat.'),
(8370, 163, '_content_8_slides_10_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8371, 163, 'content_8_slides_11_img', '112'),
(8372, 163, '_content_8_slides_11_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8373, 163, 'content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'Irasema'),
(8374, 163, '_content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8375, 163, 'content_8_slides_11_sub', ''),
(8376, 163, '_content_8_slides_11_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8377, 163, 'content_8_slides_11_txt', 'Irasema currently works as a coach specialized in pilates reformer as well as pilates mat. Her focus has always been to connect the body with the mind efficiently and dynamically, seeking to provide students with the best possible experience. The greatest satisfaction she gets from teaching her classes is seeing the smiles on her students\' faces.'),
