(8836, 165, '_content_8_slides_10_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8837, 165, 'content_8_slides_10_txt', 'Eugenia was trained under the Pilates Teacher Certification program. As an instructor, she aims to strengthen and correct through control, based on repetition, control, and precision. Her classic class is based on authentic Pilates, while flow and burn are a combination of both classic and contemporary, both in Mat and Reformer.'),
(8838, 165, '_content_8_slides_10_txt', 'field_65e65a1d9a31b'),
(8839, 165, 'content_8_slides_11_img', '112'),
(8840, 165, '_content_8_slides_11_img', 'field_65e659d69a318'),
(8841, 165, 'content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'Irasema Ledesma'),
(8842, 165, '_content_8_slides_11_ttl', 'field_65e659e99a319'),
(8843, 165, 'content_8_slides_11_sub', ''),
(8844, 165, '_content_8_slides_11_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(8845, 165, 'content_8_slides_11_txt', 'Irasema\'s experience includes international certifications in a wide range of disciplines. Currently, she works as a specialized coach in Pilates Reformer, Mat and in personalized training, integrating functional movements with Pilates Mat and Reformer.'),
