(13293, 224, '_content_8_slides_12_sub', 'field_65e65a109a31a'),
(13294, 224, 'content_8_slides_12_txt', 'Endorsed by the Publish Health Department in prenatal movement and physical activation techniques, degenerative chronic conditions, and the general public. Performer and instructor of contemporary Pilates utilizing musicality, rhythmic memory and craneo sacral  mobility as fundamental tools.'),
